headline: 2 Reasons to Like ULTA and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, Ulta has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 20.5%. Its stock price has climbed to $670.25, representing a healthy 27.8% increase. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
